// Seed populates the database with deterministic demo data.
//
// Properties of this seed:
//   - Reads DATABASE_URL through the same config loader the services use; no hardcoded fallback.
//   - Idempotent: every record has a deterministic UUID and uses ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE,
//     so re-running updates fields without creating duplicates and without losing user-generated
//     data created on top of the seed.
//   - Transactional: nothing is committed unless the whole seed succeeds.
//   - Engagement (likes, comments, saves, notifications) is generated by joining real tables —
//     no hardcoded references to randomly-generated post UUIDs.
//
// Run:  go run ./cmd/seed
package main

